3. OBJECTS & DATA
========================================================
type: section

Everything is an object in R!  



Data Types
=========================================================

**Numeric**

```{r}
my_sum <- 3+3

class(my_sum)
print(my_sum)
```

------

**Character**

```{r}
my_daughter <- "Kat"

class(my_daughter)
my_daughter
```

Data Types Cont. 
=========================================================

**Vector**

```{r}
my_vector <- c(1,2,3,4)

class(my_vector)
print(my_vector)
```

------

**List**

```{r}
my_list <- c(1,"Kat", 3)

class(my_list)
my_list
```

Data Types Cont. 
=========================================================

**Matrix**

```{r}
my_matrix <- matrix(1:9, nrow = 3, ncol = 3)

print(my_matrix)
```

------

**Data Frame**

```{r}
my_df <- cars



head(my_df)
```

<!--Text comment-->

