Objects Concluded
=========================================================

Aside from being a certain ***class***, objects can have have other attributes, such column names and dimensions:
```{r}
colnames(my_df)
dim(my_df)
```

And can even be used with operators! Try this:

```{r, eval = F}
my_sum * my_matrix
```


